en_213295_0	Troops of 1 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) of the 573 Brigade under the 57 Division on the directions of General Officer Commanding, 57 Division, Major General Pradeep de Silva and under the supervision of the Commander 573 Brigade carried out a cleaning project in the Kandawalai Hospital premises.
en_213295_1	Officers and Other Ranks of the 573 Brigade in liaison with members of the hospital staff and civilians in the area took part in the project.
